## Tech Credits

This site is made with Eleventy - credit goes out to the people at the Eleventy community Discord for technical support, as well as the Frontend Horse Discord for general community support. CSS is [preprocessed by SASS](https://helloyes.dev/blog/2021/minimal-sass-and-eleventy-setup/), using the BIOS (BEM + ITCSS + OOCSS + SMACSS) Methodology. The font was subset with glyphhanger.